# Countdown Bot

This is a Discord bot designed to keep track of a recurring event that happens every 72 hours. It updates its status frequently to display the remaining hours until the next event, and changes its nickname to the day and time of the next event when the reset occurs.

![Problem illustration](./images/problem.png)
*Illustration of the problem the bot is designed to solve.*

![Solution illustration](./images/solution.png)
*Illustration of how the bot solves the problem.*

## Usage

To use this bot, invite it to your Discord server and give it the "Change Nickname" permission. The bot will automatically start counting down to the next event.

## Contributing

Contributions are welcome! Please feel free to submit a pull request or open an issue if you have any improvements or bug fixes.